25|$|A triple {{homicide}} {{was committed}} in Waltham, Massachusetts, {{on the evening}} of September 11, 2011. Brendan Mess, Erik Weissman, and Raphael Teken were murdered in Mess's apartment. All had their throats slit from ear to ear, with such great force that they were nearly decapitated. Thousands of dollars' worth of marijuana and money were left covering their mutilated bodies, and $5,000 was left at the scene. The local district <b>attorney</b> <b>said</b> that it appeared that the killer and the victims knew each other, and that the murders were not random.|$|E
